videos.description: Trestan Ebner recovers a fumble for Baylor in the end zone to take an early lead over Oklahoma State.
videos.headline: Right place right time for Baylor

videos.description: Timarcus Davis recovers a Jalen McCleskey fumble on a punt to put Baylor in scoring position.
videos.headline: Davis recovers muffed punt from McCleskey

videos.description: Mason Rudolph finds Marcell Ateman for the 38-yard touchdown to tie the game 7-7.
videos.headline: Ateman breaks away for 38-yard score

videos.description: Mason Rudolph delivers a perfect strike to Jalen McCleskey for the 25-yard score.
videos.headline: Rudolph threads the needle for the TD

videos.description: Justice Hill gets loose and shows off his speed for the 79-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Hill busts out for for 79-yard TD run

videos.description: Mason Rudolph finishes the drive with a 1-yard touchdown run.
videos.headline: Rudolph keeps it for the TD

videos.description: Mason Rudolph finds James Washington over the middle for a 68-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Washington gets into the open field for the 68-yard TD

videos.description: James Washington get into the end zone for the second time on the day.
videos.headline: Washington takes it in from 2 yards out

videos.description: Oklahoma State backup QB Taylor Cornelius  takes off for the 40-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Cornelius dashes for the 40-yard TD
